36
00:05:22,488 --> 00:05:24,156
Could be.

37
00:05:24,156 --> 00:05:26,156
Boy, you'd think they'd at least
air-condition these places.

38
00:05:26,158 --> 00:05:29,158
- What is your name, sir?
