I'll be right outside the door.

42
00:05:36,836 --> 00:05:39,601
- Just knock.
- Okay, thanks. We will.

43
00:05:51,601 --> 00:05:52,601
Good morning.

44
00:05:52,894 --> 00:05:54,437
I never knew they locked the door.

45
00:05:54,437 --> 00:05:56,437
Sure they lock the door.
What'd you think?

46
00:05:57,690 --> 00:06:00,690
I don't know.
It just never occurred to me.

47
00:06:01,737 --> 00:06:03,613
What's that for?

48
00:06:03,613 --> 00:06:05,574
Oh, I thought we might want
to vote by ballot.

49
00:06:05,574 --> 00:06:08,495
Great idea. Maybe we can
get him elected senator.

50
00:06:10,495 --> 00:06:12,495
Just in case, you know.

51
00:06:15,750 --> 00:06:17,750
- Î—ow'd you like it?
